    <h1>Rich Results</h1>
    <p class="description">Enhanced search listings that show star ratings, prices, FAQs, images, and more — powered by structured data. Rich results <strong>increase SERP real estate and click-through rates</strong> without requiring higher rankings.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
